com.ece.superkids.users.entities

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ece.superkids.users.entities.State
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class State
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The State class represents the current state of the user. It holds all the information for current level, category, and scores map from questions to scores.
    Author:
    Marc Adam
